    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You cast spells like a disciple, gaining a spellbook with four common arcanima cantrips of your choice. You gain the Cast a Spell activity. You can prepare two cantrips each day from your spellbook. Each time you gain a spell slot of a new level from the disciple archetype, add a spell of that level or lower to your spellbook. You're trained in arcanima spell attack rolls and spell DCs. Your key spellcasting ability for disciple archetype spells is Intelligence, and they are arcanima disciple spells.</p><p>You become trained in your choice of Arcana or Crafting; if you were already trained in both of these skills, you instead become trained in a skill of your choice. You also gain the gift of the land disciple class feature, except you do not gain the saving throws.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.journals.JournalEntry.ZDsnoPK15uLTpQG8.JournalEntryPage.difsnGNg3Im9ZtWH]{Disciple}</p>",
